{
  "_doc": [
    "Fixture for the PoC Anomaly Review Workshop dashboard.",
    "",
    "Three pages, each is a list of section widgets (children) that hold the leaf",
    "widgets the WorkshopEditorPage already supports: object_table, filter_list,",
    "object_set_title, button_group, property_list, chart_pie, chart_xy.",
    "",
    "Variables wire object set definitions (one per backing Iceberg table) +",
    "filter outputs + active-object handles. Buttons reference action types by id.",
    "",
    "How to load:",
    "  1) Open the OpenFoundry web frontend (`kubectl port-forward web 8080:80`).",
    "  2) The /apps backend is not yet wired in this cluster, so the editor",
    "     persists drafts in browser localStorage (key prefix `of:workshop:`).",
    "     Create an app with the WorkshopEditor, choose 'Save as...', and on the",
    "     Settings tab paste this JSON into the `Workshop variables` import slot.",
    "  3) Alternatively, when the AppBuilder service lands, this JSON can be POSTed",
    "     verbatim to /api/v1/apps with `name=poc-anomaly-review`."
  ],
  "name": "PoC — Anomaly Review",
  "slug": "poc-anomaly-review",
  "description": "Order anomaly review dashboard backed by 4 Iceberg tables in lakekeeper.default",
  "status": "draft",
  "settings": {
    "workshop_header": {
      "title": "Anomaly Review",
      "icon": "shield",
      "color": "#cf923f"
    },
    "workshop_header_ui": {
      "enable_module_header": true,
      "custom_color": true,
      "enable_app_logo": true,
      "logo_kind": "icon",
      "enable_favoriting": true,
      "image_url": ""
    },
    "workshop_variables": [
      {
        "id": "var_transactions",
        "kind": "object_set",
        "name": "All transactions",
        "object_type_id": "678b55fe-db5f-4d3a-bbf2-8cb643af8d32"
      },
      {
        "id": "var_anomalies",
      "kind": "object_set_definition",
      "name": "Anomalies only (review_status = needs_review)",
      "object_type_id": "678b55fe-db5f-4d3a-bbf2-8cb643af8d32",
      "static_filter": {
        "property_name": "review_status",
        "operator": "equals",
        "value": "needs_review"
      },
      "filter_variable_id": "var_filter_anomalies"
    },
      {
        "id": "var_customers",
        "kind": "object_set",
        "name": "All customers",
        "object_type_id": "46e2598c-0d11-4ab2-a4aa-301f3e8fb5a7"
      },
      {
        "id": "var_filter_anomalies",
        "kind": "filter_output",
        "name": "Anomaly filter output",
        "object_type_id": "678b55fe-db5f-4d3a-bbf2-8cb643af8d32",
        "source_widget_id": "filter_anomalies"
      },
      {
        "id": "var_active_tx",
        "kind": "object_set_active_object",
        "name": "Active transaction",
        "object_type_id": "678b55fe-db5f-4d3a-bbf2-8cb643af8d32",
        "source_widget_id": "tbl_anomalies"
      },
      {
        "id": "var_active_customer",
        "kind": "object_set_active_object",
        "name": "Active customer",
        "object_type_id": "46e2598c-0d11-4ab2-a4aa-301f3e8fb5a7",
        "source_widget_id": "tbl_customers"
      }
    ]
  },
